00:38:44.781 --> 00:38:49.369
You know.
but outside that environment‐‐

922
00:38:49.494 --> 00:38:50.995
‐ Shawn Michaels.
British Bulldog.

923
00:38:51.120 --> 00:38:52.831
<i>1‐2‐3 Kid walk into a bar.</i>

