00:39:21.651 --> 00:39:24.654
and leave him in the side
of the car.

937
00:39:24.737 --> 00:39:26.489
‐ <i>And the last
thing I can remember is.</i>

938
00:39:26.614 --> 00:39:28.241
<i>you know.
there being the coat check.</i>

